===========================================================================
$NetBSD$

If you plan to use SQL for authentication and/or accouting, install 
databases/p5-DBI and the relevant Perl DBD driver.

If you plan to use MS-CHAP/MS-CHAP2, install security/p5-Digest-MD4.

If you plan to use LDAP for authentication and/or accounting, install 
databases/p5-perl-ldap.

If you plan to use EAP TLS, TTLS or PEAP for 802.1x authentication, install 
security/p5-Net_SSLeay, security/p5-Digest-HMAC and
security/p5-Digest-SHA1.

If you plan to use the GUI interface to radpwtst obtain and install 
x11/p5-Tk.

===========================================================================
